{"id":82,"ayahs":[{"number":24,"arabic":"۞ وَٱلْمُحْصَنَٰتُ مِنَ ٱلنِّسَآءِ إِلَّا مَا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَٰنُكُمْ ۖ كِتَٰبَ ٱللَّهِ عَلَيْكُمْ ۚ وَأُحِلَّ لَكُم مَّا وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكُمْ أَن تَبْتَغُوا۟ بِأَمْوَٰلِكُم مُّحْصِنِينَ غَيْرَ مُسَٰفِحِينَ ۚ فَمَا ٱسْتَمْتَعْتُم بِهِۦ مِنْهُنَّ فَـَٔاتُوهُنَّ أُجُورَهُنَّ فَرِيضَةًۭ ۚ وَلَا جُنَاحَ عَلَيْكُمْ فِيمَا تَرَٰضَيْتُم بِهِۦ مِنۢ بَعْدِ ٱلْفَرِيضَةِ ۚ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ كَانَ عَلِيمًا حَكِيمًۭا","translation":"And [forbidden to you are] all married women other than those whom you rightfully possess [through wedlock]: this is God's ordinance, binding upon you. But lawful to you are all [women] beyond these, for you to seek out, offering them of your possessions, taking them in honest wedlock, and not in fornication. And unto those with whom you desire to enjoy marriage, you shall give the dowers due to them; but you will incur no sin if, after [having agreed upon] this lawful due, you freely agree with one another upon anything [else]: behold, God is indeed all-knowing, wise.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/517.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":26590,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ وَٱلْمُحْصَنَـٰتُ","translation":"এবং (বিবাহ নিষিদ্ধ) (অন্যের) বিবাহাধীন নারীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26591,"position":2,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26592,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلنِّسَآءِ","translation":"স্ত্রীলোকদের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26593,"position":4,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ব্যতীত","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26594,"position":5,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26595,"position":6,"arabic":"مَلَكَتْ","translation":"মালিক হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26596,"position":7,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنُكُمْ ۖ","translation":"তোমাদের ডান হাত (অর্থাৎ যুদ্ধ বন্দিনী)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26598,"position":8,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبَ","translation":"নির্দেশ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26599,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26600,"position":10,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ ۚ","translation":"তোমাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26602,"position":11,"arabic":"وَأُحِلَّ","translation":"এবং হালাল করা হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26603,"position":12,"arabic":"لَكُم","translation":"তোমাদের জন্য","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26604,"position":13,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা (আছে নারী)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26605,"position":14,"arabic":"وَرَآءَ","translation":"ব্যতীত","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26606,"position":15,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكُمْ","translation":"এসব","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26607,"position":16,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"(এশর্তে) যে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26608,"position":17,"arabic":"تَبْتَغُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা চাইবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26609,"position":18,"arabic":"بِأَمْوَٰلِكُم","translation":"তোমাদের ধন-মাল দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26610,"position":19,"arabic":"مُّحْصِنِينَ","translation":"বিবাহবন্ধনে আবদ্ধ হবে (হিসেবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26611,"position":20,"arabic":"غَيْرَ","translation":"নয়","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26612,"position":21,"arabic":"مُسَـٰفِحِينَ ۚ","translation":"ব্যভিচারী হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26614,"position":22,"arabic":"فَمَا","translation":"অতঃপর যা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26615,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱسْتَمْتَعْتُم","translation":"তোমরা সম্ভোগ কর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26616,"position":24,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"তা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26617,"position":25,"arabic":"مِنْهُنَّ","translation":"তাদের মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26618,"position":26,"arabic":"فَـَٔاتُوهُنَّ","translation":"সেজন্য তাদেরকে দাও","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26619,"position":27,"arabic":"أُجُورَهُنَّ","translation":"মোহরানা তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26620,"position":28,"arabic":"فَرِيضَةًۭ ۚ","translation":"ফরজ (হিসেবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26622,"position":29,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং নাই","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26623,"position":30,"arabic":"جُنَاحَ","translation":"কোন দোষ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26624,"position":31,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26625,"position":32,"arabic":"فِيمَا","translation":"ঐবিষয়ে যা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26626,"position":33,"arabic":"تَرَٰضَيْتُم","translation":"তোমরা পরস্পর রাজী হও","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26627,"position":34,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"তা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26628,"position":35,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"(থেকে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26629,"position":36,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26630,"position":37,"arabic":"ٱلْفَرِيضَةِ ۚ","translation":"মোহর নির্ধারণের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_042.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26632,"position":38,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_044.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26633,"position":39,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_045.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26634,"position":40,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"হলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_046.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26635,"position":41,"arabic":"عَلِيمًا","translation":"সর্বজ্ঞ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_047.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26636,"position":42,"arabic":"حَكِيمًۭا","translation":"প্রজ্ঞাময়","audioUrl":"wbw/004_024_048.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":26637,"position":43,"arabic":"٢٤","translation":"(২৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":25,"arabic":"وَمَن لَّمْ يَسْتَطِعْ مِنكُمْ طَوْلًا أَن يَنكِحَ ٱلْمُحْصَنَٰتِ ٱلْمُؤْمِنَٰتِ فَمِن مَّا مَلَكَتْ أَيْمَٰنُكُم مِّن فَتَيَٰتِكُمُ ٱلْمُؤْمِنَٰتِ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ أَعْلَمُ بِإِيمَٰنِكُم ۚ بَعْضُكُم مِّنۢ بَعْضٍۢ ۚ فَٱنكِحُوهُنَّ بِإِذْنِ أَهْلِهِنَّ وَءَاتُوهُنَّ أُجُورَهُنَّ بِٱلْمَعْرُوفِ مُحْصَنَٰتٍ غَيْرَ مُسَٰفِحَٰتٍۢ وَلَا مُتَّخِذَٰتِ أَخْدَانٍۢ ۚ فَإِذَآ أُحْصِنَّ فَإِنْ أَتَيْنَ بِفَٰحِشَةٍۢ فَعَلَيْهِنَّ نِصْفُ مَا عَلَى ٱلْمُحْصَنَٰتِ مِنَ ٱلْعَذَابِ ۚ ذَٰلِكَ لِمَنْ خَشِىَ ٱلْعَنَتَ مِنكُمْ ۚ وَأَن تَصْبِرُوا۟ خَيْرٌۭ لَّكُمْ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ غَفُورٌۭ رَّحِيمٌۭ","translation":"And as for those of you who, owing to cir­cumstances, are not in a position to marry free believing women, [let them marry] believing maidens from among those whom you rightfully possess. And God knows all about your faith; each one of you is an issue of the other. Marry them, then, with their people's leave, and give them their dowers in an equitable manner - they being women who give themselves in honest wedlock, not in fornication, nor as secret love-companions. And when they are married, and thereafter become guilty of immoral conduct, they shall be liable to half the penalty to which free married women are liable. This [permission to marry slave-girls applies] to those of you who fear lest they stumble into evil. But it is for your own good to persevere in patience [and to abstain from such marriages]: and God is much-forgiving, a dispenser of grace.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/518.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":27613,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَن","translation":"এবং যে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27614,"position":2,"arabic":"لَّمْ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27615,"position":3,"arabic":"يَسْتَطِعْ","translation":"সামর্থ্য রাখে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27616,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27617,"position":5,"arabic":"طَوْلًا","translation":"উপকরণের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27618,"position":6,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27619,"position":7,"arabic":"يَنكِحَ","translation":"বিবাহ করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27620,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْمُحْصَنَـٰتِ","translation":"স্বাধীনা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27621,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنَـٰتِ","translation":"মু'মিনা নারীকে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27622,"position":10,"arabic":"فَمِن","translation":"মধ্য হতে তবে (বিবাহ করবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27623,"position":11,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27624,"position":12,"arabic":"مَلَكَتْ","translation":"মালিক হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27625,"position":13,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنُكُم","translation":"তোমাদের ডান হাত সমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/004_025_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":27626,"p